Package: energyEfficiency
Title: Statistical Analysis of Building Energy Efficiency
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Marvis", "Osazuwa",
           email = "marvis.osazuwa@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible statistical analysis of building energy
    efficiency data. Provides functions for loading and validating
    building geometry data, computing descriptive statistics and
    correlations, fitting linear regression models for heating and
    cooling loads, running diagnostics for collinearity, normality,
    and heteroscedasticity, and producing publication quality plots.
